# =============================================================================
# Usage Instructions:
# =============================================================================
# 1. Copy this file: cp terraform.tfvars.example terraform.tfvars
# 2. Modify the values in terraform.tfvars according to your needs
# 3. Ensure AWS credentials are configured:
#    - AWS CLI: aws configure
#    - Environment variables: AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID, AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY
#    - IAM roles (if running on EC2)
# 4. Run: make bootstrap PROFILE=aws
# 5. Update kubeconfig: aws eks update-kubeconfig --region us-west-2 --name comind-ops-dev
# 6. Access your cluster: kubectl get nodes
